data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING 3K IN CLOSING COSTS! 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and over 2700 sq. ft of pure bliss! This property has so many updates including: updated bathrooms, new laminate & tile flooring, mud room, laundry room, tankless water heater and a HUGE 4th bedroom! Out back enjoy the inground pool, backyard with irrigation system, newly laid asphalt parking pad, covered patio and a 30x30 shop! The possibilities are endless. Seller is also open to renting for $2600/mo.
